IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. GOTO-COMPUTABLE-EXITS-PERFORM-THROUGH.

DATA DIVISION.
01 TARGET-FIELD PICTURE IS X(20).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
DISPLAY "MAIN BEFORE PERFORM"
PERFORM FIRST THROUGH SECOND
DISPLAY "MAIN AFTER PERFORM".

FIRST.
MOVE "OUTSIDE" TO TARGET-FIELD
DISPLAY "FIRST BEFORE COMPUTED GOTO"
GO TO TARGET-FIELD.

SECOND.
DISPLAY "SECOND SHOULD NOT RUN".

OUTSIDE.
DISPLAY "OUTSIDE COMPUTED TARGET"
STOP.
